    "body": "IIRC, `--profile-dir` allow you to set the directory in which the profile are **searched** but it is not what I want, I want to explicitely pass **the profile** basicaly I woudl like the ability to merge:\n\n``` bash\n$ ipyton --ProfileDir.location=~/.ipython/ --profile=default\n```\n\nInto one option\n\n``` bash\n$ ipython --with-profile=~/.ipython/profile_default\n```\n"
